n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#92CDDC;\"></span><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/IldMRDMKHALNMrPgclpMN7sDVmS81ezVOibGEFUIxKyUMQibnibOdUhqIccltaTXvrPwM3C1Gr1icyzaFlD8iaiaAEfQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" width=\"auto\" style=\"width:auto !important;\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#00B0F0;font-size:13.33px;font-weight:bold;\">长按二维码</span><span style=\"color:#4BACC6;font-size:13.33px;font-weight:bold;\">点选（识别图中二维码）</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"color:#4BACC6;font-size:13.33px;font-weight:bold;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>','[weixin]http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/DW85l9zfVpacMYa9IErYAWvUFzQrOxsLdextiaYasVpw6SSOlPElIjPF31ticeRIkx1DQKWJ8Jl57gP58y4GQujA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg','18','0','-1','0.05','2015-8-17');");
E_D("replace into `article` values('86','0','五十款型男发型，要与你的发型师好好聊聊','<p>\r\n	<strong><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/R7658nOCdh9Sib3GpyiaypfJmeW0zAxnbFnkKn2UStlLgeeEibhuQpic7JCla5Ke3Xtklmic6L5PEArbAJLicIhibRQicw/0\" /><br />\r\n</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#FF0000;line-height:1em;font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:24px;\">第1款</span><span>结构感较强的抓发</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;font-size:12px;\">一个结构感较强的，叛逆的手抓发型，必定在 2015 年开年为你赢得更多小粉丝。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/iarBRgphE1yCicDib0XibUzX8zST42OdnybWOyn3eEwE9IBYDjLPBA84p5DZd6jzzH7ia5No5BpkEu3RpVIjD58vl5A/0?wxfrom=5\" width=\"auto\" style=\"width:auto !important;\" /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;font-size:12px;\">要打造这样的发型，一定要彻底清洁你的头发，决不能有任何一丝油腻，必须是100%干净。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"line-height:1em;font-family:times, serif;font-size:42px;\">“ <span style=\"color:#FF0000;line-height:1em;font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:24px;\">第2款</span></span></strong><span>城市骚年的改良油头</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;font-size:12px;\">改良后的油头，更加的风流倜傥与精致，绝对是吸睛的造型！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/iarBRgphE1yCicDib0XibUzX8zST42OdnybWYlkMTdp95AqDfibwmpUcezbicOr4K0mNI4jhK91Z0MfLiazot3xpGtAAw/0?wxfrom=5\" width=\"auto\" style=\"width:auto !important;\" /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;font-size:12px;\">梳油头既能搭配商务西装，休闲逛街也绝对是人群中的焦点，同时你还不必担心早上起来头发会翘起来，只需把头发吹顺，涂上造型品即可。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;font-size:12px;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14.54px;\">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/iarBRgphE1yCicDib0XibUzX8zST42OdnybWDO6jOpYOWOb5hsqbxOAOiaCacV3IajF4RmNkudTdyDaS2cibrDynU2Jw/0?wxfrom=5\" width=\"auto\" style=\"width:auto !important;\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;font-size:12px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:1em;font-family:times, serif;font-size:42px;\">“ <span style=\"color:#FF0000;line-height:1em;font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:24px;\">第3款</span></span></strong><span>健康干净的长发造型</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;font-size:12px;\">一般情况下，男生的长发造型会比女生更持久，原因是女生总是喜欢用手去拨弄头发。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14.54px;\">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/iarBRgphE1yCicDib0XibUzX8zST42OdnybWKS0lKeVv3lZFonfq9ECvibvpk5m0EFxCw3FrMbexoQytib2Su2tfmz6w/0?wxfrom=5\" width=\"auto\" style=\"width:auto !important;\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;font-size:12px;\">长发是一种态度与个性，但一定要保持清洁哦！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:1em;font-family:times, serif;font-size:42px;\">“ <span style=\"color:#FF0000;line-height:1em;font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:24px;\">第4款</span></span></strong><span>男生也可以扎起丸子头</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;font-size:12px;\">到了 2015 年，骚年玩什么？玩反串呀！所有女生玩得好的，骚年怎么能认输，丸子头骚年们照样可以驾驭得 “头头” 是道。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;font-size:12px;\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/iarBRgphE1yCicDib0XibUzX8zST42OdnybWUoIrWVoNIoErj3J9KCD5iahcLcugc0kKzXGm5iaeCic9m3mJAXvk1ZqOw/0?wxfrom=5\" width=\"auto\" style=\"width:auto !important;\" /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;font-size:12px;\">留起长发的骚年每天长发披肩也许会无聊，天气热了也会受不了，那么干脆扎起一个小马辫，挽成一个丸子头吧。真的是 man 爆了好吗！谁说会娘的。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:1em;font-family:times, serif;font-size:42px;\">“ <span style=\"color:#FF0000;line-height:1em;font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:24px;\">第5款</span></span></strong><span>用发带塑造运动造型</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;font-size:12px;\">如果你不想脏头发盖住刘海弄坏你的肌肤，不想汗水沾湿你的秀发，都可以选择发带。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/iarBRgphE1yCicDib0XibUzX8zST42OdnybWficialIZx64iceGGuxIWCDIDKICTtG5yNqnPnRXPJ385PGa2WPmEuvfAw/0?wxfrom=5\" width=\"auto\" style=\"width:auto !important;\" /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#7F7F7F;font-size:12px;\">发带造型搭配牛仔裤，就可以轻松打造休闲不羁的魅力形象了。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#0070C0;\">还不够？！不要紧，主页君继续放送数十款超赞的发型图片，好让你和你的发型师好好聊聊。总有一款符合你们的Taste~</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/icqve28ZKeuVl6I59TOq03XA4ys7Z2AkXwYmqDwlp852QauNAJ8VwNJ7YmFMkDy6tgSboyalt0nibjSsZsOeUwsA/0?wxfrom=5\" width=\"auto\" style=\"width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/icqve28ZKeuVl6I59TOq03XA4ys7Z2AkXBfkpzGjffQOicNOsj0iaPOca2GjUzxRvPxOfByLKDmMo4ZuchV10icDNQ/0?wxfrom=5\" width=\"auto\" style=\"width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/icqve28ZKeuVl6I59TOq03XA4ys7Z2AkXRdGREVGt2C5wF81bIsPt8jkbr70WBGiboPUhdK39pmSfowploKmRicUg/0?wxfrom=5\" width=\"auto\" style=\"width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/icqve28ZKeuVl6I59TOq03XA4ys7Z2AkX0COw192ws9xhDXHb9QwOHBCxlReVwIKyXhB9ANfzE23ub8jeyOxwfQ/0?wxfrom=5\" width=\"auto\" style=\"width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/icqve28ZKeuVl6I59TOq03XA4ys7Z2AkX9BurcdDfVejQXgrevBu7tZdv2HlvHmqrpmkld9fGEmoJ0dpYs6xZjQ/0?wxfrom=5\" width=\"auto\" style=\"width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/icqve28ZKeuVl6I59TOq03XA4ys7Z2AkXz7ibUsiaIxDvPCLgic6gP8KfE4MadNG2kTojdtDeUpdRuMtyHxUBxd1Hw/0?wxfrom=5\" width=\"auto\" style=\"width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"http://mm